items.title: The Automatic Transmission
items.headline: A breakdown and explanation of the automatic transmission.
objectives_summary: In this course students will learn the anatomy of the automatic transmission and be able to disassemble a unit.
This course is designed to give the basic components of the transmission and explain how they work together in the unit to make the vehicle move.
This is will not tell you everything about every transmission but, it gives a blueprint to disassembling most units on the market today.
